  "identifier": "SB 45",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to agritourism.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 247.801 to amend the definition of \"agritourism activity\"; define \"working animal\"; create a new section of KRS 247.800 to 247.810 to prohibit a city, town, county, or other political subdivision of the Commonwealth from restricting a person from engaging in an agritourism activity; require that an agritourism activity comply with public health and safety requirements and any existing law enforceable by police powers of local government.",
